n quite old really, he was about fifty. And he kept his youth in a way, but my - my mother - aged young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 Where did your father come from?
