\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 Did he have any part time jobs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12212030 RW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 No, no, nothing. Yes, and I remember, you know, In that period I only saw my father on Friday nights.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 You mean he lived up at the quarry?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12212030 RW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 No, no. No. But the train didn\rquote t get into Traws \lquote 
til quarter to seven in the evening, and he started out at quarter to six in the morning, so we\rquote d gone to bed in the evenings and hadn\rquote t got up in the morning. But 
on Friday nights we could say up because it was Saturday the next day. But apart from that we didn\rquote t see him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 Do you ever remember your father being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12212030 RW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 No, no, never. Well I do remember him being injured and I do remember when the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
