\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 There was no dole or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12212030 RW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 No, no, nothing - nothing like that. Yes, but he did go and guild walls for the farmer
s, he was very good at making dry stone walls and he wasn\rquote t paid or anything but - he got his food and things like that. Potatoes and things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417384 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12408339\charrsid11292576 Did you say your mother was about fifty when you were born?
